		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Speaking of 4-bit, I remember users opinions like this ('Atari 2600 is 4-bit'), and how I was wondering if there are really any console with 4-bit CPU. As far as I know, there were no TV consoles, but Game&amp;Watch (Soviet clones, at least) actually have 4-bit MCU.<br /><br />Another interesting thing in this regard is that popular 8-bit Z80 CPU, used in many systems, has 4-bit ALU internally.

		

